{"title_page": "Chongqing Liangjiang New Area", "text_new": "{{More citations needed|date=August 2014}}\n\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- See Template:Infobox settlement for additional fields and descriptions -->\n<!-- Basic info  ---------------->\n|name                   = Liangjiang New Area\n|official_name          = Chongqing Liangjiang New Area\n|other_name             = \n|native_name            = {{lower|0.1em|{{nobold|{{lang|zh-hans|\u4e24\u6c5f\u65b0\u533a}}}}}}\n|nickname               = \n|settlement_type        =[[New areas|State-level new area]]\n|total_type             = <!-- to set a non-standard label for total area and population rows -->\n|motto                  = \n<!-- images and maps  ----------->\n|image_skyline          = Chongqing - View 03.jpg\n|imagesize              = \n|image_caption          = [[Jiangbeizui CBD]] (\u6c5f\u5317\u5634\u91d1\u878d\u4e2d\u5fc3)\n|image_flag             = \n|flag_size              = \n|image_seal             = \n|seal_size              = \n|image_shield           = \n|shield_size            = \n|image_blank_emblem     = \n|blank_emblem_type      = \n|blank_emblem_size      = \n|image_map              = Liangjiang New Area.svg\n|mapsize                = 250px\n|map_caption            = Liangjiang New Area in Chongqing\n|image_map1             = \n|mapsize1               = \n|map_caption1           = \n|image_dot_map          = \n|dot_mapsize            = \n|dot_map_caption        = \n|dot_x                  = \n|dot_y                  = \n|coor_pinpoint          = Liangjiang administrative committee\n|coordinates            = {{Coord|29.6426|N|106.5670|E|region:CN-50_source:Gaode|format=dms|display=it}}\n<!-- Location ------------------>\n|subdivision_type       = [[List of sovereign states|Country]]\n|subdivision_name       = [[China|People's Republic of China]]\n|subdivision_type1      = [[Direct-administered municipalities of China|Municipality]]\n|subdivision_name1      = [[Chongqing]]\n|subdivision_type2    