10 years\u201d.{{citation needed|date=August 2014}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.liangjiang.gov.cn/ Liangjiang New Area official website]\n\n{{Chongqing}}\n{{New Area}}\n\n[[Category:New areas (China)]]\n[[Category:2010 establishments in China]]\n[[Category:Economy of Chongqing]]\n[[Category:Geography of Chongqing]]\n", "name_user": "Xindeho", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chongqing_Liangjiang_New_Area"}
